The Az 1 TeamCoord has invited you to access the medical information of Mr John Patient so you can help manage their health.

Message from The Az 1 TeamCoord

Please consider being my carer

To accept this invitation, click this link:

http://pkb-frontend-9/patient/accept.action?invitationId=9f69b2a4-463f-46da-b402-f44938dd5752&e=az.patient.3%40pkbtest.com

You are receiving this notification because you are a carer. To log in and review the people you care for, please click this link: "http://pkb-frontend-9/patient/myDependents.action?tab=invitations&subTab=dependents"

Please do not reply to this email; this address is not monitored. Log into your record to manage your care and those whom you care for.

Yours,

Patients Know Best Help Team
